"A.P.238/4/9/13:00": "That's enough! The winner is Claris Claes!"
"Hm, so you finally get to see it for yourself. This is the power of the council of six."
"But I have to praise you for not sucking peon. It's been a while since I've actually had to try."
"Thanks for the fight! I was able to enjoy myself. Now I'm going to sleep!"
"Well then peon, try and work harder for the next time we fight again!"
"Ah, too bad! But for fighting up to this point you were at a disadvantage!"
"Even so, great effort! I really enjoyed watching you struggle!"
"I hope you enjoyed the opportunity to face off against someone in the Council of Six!"
"I look forward to seeing you grow even stronger! Now if you'll excuse me!"
